<div class="container marketing">
	<center><h1> Software Development </h1></center>
	<br><br>
	<center><h2>Project Motivation</h2></center>
	<br>
	<p>
	Software development in the CBL covers multiple aspects including processing tools to facilitate the preparation of raw experimental and clinical data, such as the processing of multi-lead ECG data and geometrical modeling tools using homographic scans, as well as GPU based acceleration of data-driven modeling and inference algorithms developed in the lab.
  	<p>

